OL,3,CWelsh museum says 'no decisions' have
OL,4,Cbeen made about closing after
OL,5,Cspeculation
OL,7,FNational Museum Wales has said 'no
OL,8,Fdecisions' have been made on its
OL,9,Fclosure after online speculation
OL,10,Fsuggested the site could shut for 'a
OL,11,Fminimum of 4 years' for redevelopment.
OL,13,FIt comes after an online post claimed
OL,14,Fthat the museum could close for 'at
OL,15,Fleast 4 or 5 years in 2027' for
OL,16,Frenovation works as it reaches its
OL,17,F100th anniversary.
OL,19,FThe Cardiff site temporarily closed
OL,20,Ffor maintenance back in 2025 after a
OL,21,Fmechanical issue.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
