OL,3,CWelsh museum says 'no decisions' have
OL,4,Cbeen made about closing after
OL,5,Cspeculation
OL,7,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,8,FMuseum Wales said:
OL,10,F"Maintaining a historic building of
OL,11,Fthe age, scale and complexity of
OL,12,FNational Museum Cardiff is an ongoing
OL,13,Fchallenge.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1782904686
OL,3,CWelsh museum says 'no decisions' have
OL,4,Cbeen made about closing after
OL,5,Cspeculation
OL,7,F"With the Museum approaching its
OL,8,Fcentenary next year, we are looking at
OL,9,Foptions for potential improvement and
OL,10,Fredevelopment to maintain and preserve
OL,11,Fthe building and to enhance the
OL,12,Fexperience for our visitors, ensuring
OL,13,Fit is fit for purpose for future
OL,14,Fgenerations.
OL,16,F"These exciting milestone plans are at
OL,17,Fan early stage and subject to several
OL,18,Fstages of business cases and planning
OL,19,Fframeworks - as such, no decisions
OL,20,Fhave been made yet.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
