OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1782904686
OL,3,CWelsh museum says 'no decisions' have
OL,4,Cbeen made about closing after
OL,5,Cspeculation
OL,7,F"Any planned decision to temporarily
OL,8,Fclose the Museum's building for any
OL,9,Fperiod of time will be subject to a
OL,10,Ffull review and consultation with our
OL,11,Fstaff, volunteers, visitors and the
OL,12,Fwider community, confirmed by its
OL,13,FBoard of Trustees."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
